            >The temple is a marvel of architectural design, covering a total
            area of 2.7 acres with a towering height of almost 360 ft. It is set
            to feature 12 grand gates and 3 floors, showcasing impressive
            craftsmanship and grandeur that is expected to awe visitors.</span
