            >Situated next to the Holy Sarayu River, the temple offers a serene
            and spiritual experience for visitors. The picturesque surroundings
            and the presence of holy ghats add to the cultural and spiritual
            significance of the site. Additionally, the city of Ayodhya
            organizes cultural shows and plays based on the epic Ramayana,
            providing a rich and immersive cultural experience for
            tourists.</span
